mysql_query: (SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID= B.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE =1 ) UNION ( SELECT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA B INNER JOIN CINEMA A ON A.SEAT_ID= B.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE =1 ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_S, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEA_S FROM CINEMA ) C WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (LAG_S = 1 OR LEA_S =1) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID -1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C3.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C2.FREE = 1 OR C3.FREE =1)

SELECT CINEMA.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS PREVIOUS ON CINEMA.SEAT_ID - PREVIOUS.SEAT_ID = 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS SUCCESSIVE ON SUCCESSIVE.SEAT_ID - CINEMA.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE CINEMA.FREE AND (PREVIOUS.FREE OR SUCCESSIVE.FREE) ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT (A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS (A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT T1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS T1 INNER JOIN CINEMA AS T2 ON T1.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 AND (T2.SEAT_ID = T1.SEAT_ID + 1 OR T2.SEAT_ID = T1.SEAT_ID - 1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE =1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ( A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID +1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1) OR ( A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID -1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1) AND ((A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1) OR (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1)) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID- B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID = 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE = TRUE AND C2.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C4 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C4.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE 1=1 AND ((C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) OR (C1.FREE = 1 AND C4.FREE = 1) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) AND (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) AND (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1)
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND ( ( C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 ) OR (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1) ) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C2.FREE = TRUE AND C1.FREE = TRUE
SELECT DISTINCT S.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S LEFT JOIN CINEMA S1 ON S.SEAT_ID+1=S1.SEAT_ID OR S.SEAT_ID-1=S1.SEAT_ID WHERE (S.FREE=1 AND S1.FREE=1) ORDER BY S.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT T1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS T1 INNER JOIN CINEMA AS T2 ON ABS(T1.SEAT_ID - T2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND T1.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B WHERE ((A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1) OR (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1)) AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND (A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C0 ON C0.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C0.FREE = 1 OR C2.FREE = 1)

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 INNER JOIN ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SUM(FREE) OVER( ROWS BETWEEN 1 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW ) AS SUM_FREE_B, SUM(FREE) OVER( ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 1 FOLLOWING ) AS SUM_FREE_F FROM CINEMA AS C2 ) AS C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C2.SUM_FREE_B>= 2 OR C2.SUM_FREE_F >= 2
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(*) > 0 ORDER BY 1
SELECT CINEMA.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS B ON B.SEAT_ID = CINEMA.SEAT_ID + 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C ON C.SEAT_ID = CINEMA.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE CINEMA.FREE = 1 AND (B.FREE = 1 OR C.FREE = 1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE= TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE=B.FREE AND ABS (A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 GROUP BY A.SEAT_ID ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE=B.FREE WHERE ABS (A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 GROUP BY A.SEAT_ID ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID+1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID-1 ) AND (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE=1)
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.FREE = 1) AND (C2.FREE = 1) AND (ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID)=1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID+1) AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER() AS PREV, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER() AS NEXT FROM CINEMA ) A WHERE A.FREE=1 AND (A.NEXT = 1 OR A.PREV=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY SEAT_ID - RN) AS CT FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RN FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) A ) B WHERE CT >= 2

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NXT, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE FROM CINEMA ) T WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NXT = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND PRE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) = 1 AS LEAD_FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) = 1 AS LAG_FREE FROM CINEMA ) Z WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_FREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAG_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE ,LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE FROM CINEMA )TEMP WHERE (FREE = NEXT_FREE OR FREE=PREV_FREE ) AND FREE!=0

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LEAD_FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LAG_FREE FROM CINEMA ) Z WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_FREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAG_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LAG, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LEAD FROM CINEMA ) AS T WHERE (FREE=1 AND FREE_LAG=1) OR (FREE=1 AND FREE_LEAD=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID -1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, COALESCE(LAG(FREE) OVER (), 0) PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE, COALESCE(LEAD(FREE) OVER(), 0) NEXT_SEAT_FREE FROM CINEMA) T1 WHERE T1.FREE = 1 AND (T1.PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE = 1 OR T1.NEXT_SEAT_FREE) ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID

SELECT X.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT C.SEAT_ID, C.FREE, LAG(C.FREE, 1)OVER(ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID) AS LAG_FREE, LEAD(C.FREE, 1)OVER(ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_FREE FROM CINEMA C ) AS X WHERE (X.FREE = 1 AND X.LAG_FREE = 1) OR (X.FREE = 1 AND X.LEAD_FREE = 1) ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT S1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S1 JOIN CINEMA S2 ON ABS(S1.SEAT_ID - S2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND S1.FREE = 1 AND S2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXTFREE,LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS BEFOREFREE FROM CINEMA) T WHERE ((FREE = 1 AND NEXTFREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND BEFOREFREE = 1)) ORDER BY 1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LEAD, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LAG FROM CINEMA) AS CINEMA_1 WHERE (CINEMA_1.FREE = '1') AND (CINEMA_1.FREE_LEAD = '1' OR CINEMA_1.FREE_LAG = '1') ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LEAD, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LAG FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (T.FREE = 1 AND T.FREE_LEAD = 1) OR (T.FREE = 1 AND T.FREE_LAG = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1 AND( SEAT_ID+1 IN(SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN(SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1))
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS NEXT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS PREV FROM CINEMA) A WHERE A.FREE=TRUE AND (NEXT = TRUE OR PREV=TRUE) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH 2_FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE AS C_FREE , LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS CF_FREE , LAG(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS CB_FREE FROM CINEMA ORDER BY SEAT_ID ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM 2_FREE WHERE (C_FREE = 1 AND CF_FREE = 1 ) OR (C_FREE = 1 AND CB_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, SUM(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ROWS BETWEEN 1 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS COUNT_PRECEDING, SUM(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 1 FOLLOWING) AS COUNT_FOLLOWING FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE COUNT_PRECEDING >1 OR COUNT_FOLLOWING >1

WITH T AS( ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 ) UNION ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 ) ) SELECT T.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM T ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH ADD_ROW_NUM AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS ID_DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ), ADD_COUNT AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY ID_DIFF) AS N FROM ADD_ROW_NUM ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ADD_COUNT WHERE N >= 2 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT * , SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS GROUPED_NUMBERS FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE GROUPED_NUMBERS IN (SELECT GROUPED_NUMBERS FROM CTE GROUP BY GROUPED_NUMBERS HAVING COUNT(GROUPED_NUMBERS) > 1)

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER () AS LAG_FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER () AS LEAD_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LAG_FREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, (SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS GRP FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE GRP IN (SELECT GRP FROM CTE GROUP BY GRP HAVING COUNT(SEAT_ID) >= 2)

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID-ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FLAG FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1), FLAG AS (SELECT FLAG FROM CTE GROUP BY FLAG HAVING COUNT(FLAG)>=2) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE JOIN FLAG ON CTE.FLAG=FLAG.FLAG ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE0, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE1 FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE0=1 AND FREE !=0) OR (FREE1=1 AND FREE !=0)

WITH CTE AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LG, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LD FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LG = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LD = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT LAG(SEAT_ID) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE, SEAT_ID AS CURR, LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEX FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT CURR AS SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE PRE = CURR -1 OR CURR = NEX -1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) GROUP_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM FREE WHERE GROUP_ID IN (SELECT GROUP_ID FROM FREE GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(*) >=2)

WITH PREV_NEXT_FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1, FALSE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1, FALSE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM PREV_NEXT_FREE WHERE FREE AND (PREV_FREE OR NEXT_FREE)

WITH RES AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM RES WHERE ( FREE = 1 AND PREV_FREE = 1 ) OR ( FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE = 1) ORDER BY 1

WITH SUB AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SUB WHERE ((PREV_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1) OR (NEXT_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1)) AND NOT (PREV_SEAT IS NULL AND NEXT_SEAT IS NULL) ORDER BY 1

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID, LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT_FREE, LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE, FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE ((FREE = 1) AND (NEXT_SEAT_FREE = 1)) OR ((FREE = 1) AND (PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE = 1))

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT_FREE, LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE, FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE ((FREE = 1) AND (NEXT_SEAT_FREE = 1)) OR ((FREE = 1) AND (PREVIOUS_SEAT_FREE = 1))
WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1) AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ) SELECT * FROM TEMP

SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT B.SEAT_ID, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY B.DIFF) AS CT FROM (SELECT A.SEAT_ID, (A.SEAT_ID-A.NUM) AS DIFF FROM (SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER () AS NUM FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)A ) B)C WHERE C.CT>=2
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID IN (SELECT SEAT_ID - 1 FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID IN (SELECT SEAT_ID + 1 FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) AS C1 WHERE C1.SEAT_ID +1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR C1.SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C3.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE (C1.FREE != 0) AND (C1.FREE = C2.FREE OR C1.FREE = C3.FREE)
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID LEFT JOIN CINEMA C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C3.SEAT_ID WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C2.FREE = 1 OR C3.FREE = 1)
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CINEMA C2 WHERE ((C2.SEAT_ID + 1 = C1.SEAT_ID) OR (C2.SEAT_ID - 1 = C1.SEAT_ID)) AND C2.FREE = 1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ((C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1) OR (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1)) AND (C1.FREE = 1) AND (C2.FREE = 1) GROUP BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = '1' AND C2. FREE = '1' AND ((C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID-1) OR (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID+1)) GROUP BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT (A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(B.SEAT_ID - A.SEAT_ID ) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT (A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID+1 OR B.SEAT_ID = A.SEAT_ID+1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A ,CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE =1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ((A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 OR (B.SEAT_ID - A.SEAT_ID) = 1) AND A.FREE AND B.FREE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE=TRUE AND B.FREE=TRUE AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE=TRUE AND B.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(B.SEAT_ID - A.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND (A.SEAT_ID+1 = B.SEAT_ID OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID+1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE =1 AND B.FREE=1 AND (A.SEAT_ID+1 = B.SEAT_ID OR B.SEAT_ID+1 = A.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE =1 AND (A.SEAT_ID+1=B.SEAT_ID OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID+1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A, CINEMA AS B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE =1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY B.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C JOIN CINEMA AS C1 WHERE ABS(C.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C.FREE = 1 AND C1.FREE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE=TRUE AND C2.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 WHERE (C1.FREE = C2.FREE AND C1.FREE = 1) AND (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1, CINEMA AS C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID = 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS (C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.FREE = C2.FREE AND C1.FREE = 1 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE+C2.FREE=2 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE =1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND ((C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID -1 ) OR (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID +1))
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT S1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S1 JOIN CINEMA S2 ON S1.SEAT_ID = S2.SEAT_ID+1 OR S1.SEAT_ID = S2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE S1.FREE = 1 AND S2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY S1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT S1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S1 JOIN CINEMA S2 WHERE ABS(S1.SEAT_ID - S2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND S1.FREE = 1 AND S2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE_IND, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE_FREE_IND FROM CINEMA ) AS A WHERE FREE = 1 AND (NEXT_FREE_IND = 1 OR PRE_FREE_IND = 1) ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT T1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA T1 JOIN CINEMA T2 ON (T1.SEAT_ID = T2.SEAT_ID - 1 OR T1.SEAT_ID = T2.SEAT_ID + 1) WHERE T1.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT X.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA X JOIN CINEMA Y WHERE X.FREE=1 AND Y.FREE=1 AND (Y.SEAT_ID=X.SEAT_ID+1 OR X.SEAT_ID=Y.SEAT_ID+1) ORDER BY X.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C JOIN CINEMA C1 ON ABS(C.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE =1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1) AND C2.FREE = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN (LAG(FREE) OVER () = 1 AND FREE = 1) THEN SEAT_ID WHEN (LEAD(FREE) OVER () = 1 AND FREE = 1) THEN SEAT_ID ELSE NULL END AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA) C WHERE SEAT_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE=1 )A UNION ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE=1 ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT , LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) A WHERE FREE = 1 AND (NEXT_SEAT = 1 OR PREV_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER ( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT , LAG( FREE,1) OVER ( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV FROM CINEMA ) D WHERE FREE = 1 AND (NEXT = 1 OR PREV =1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS _LAG , LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS _LEAD FROM CINEMA ) TBL WHERE TBL.FREE = 1 AND (TBL._LAG = 1 OR TBL._LEAD = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAGE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEADE FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (LAGE=1 AND FREE!=0) OR (LEADE=1 AND FREE!=0)

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(SEAT_ID,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ) AS PREV, LEAD(SEAT_ID,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) C WHERE ABS(C.PREV- SEAT_ID)=1 OR ABS(C.NEXT-SEAT_ID)=1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS LE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER() AS LA FROM CINEMA ) X WHERE FREE = 1 AND (LE = 1 OR LA = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE,LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS PREVSEAT,LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS NEXTSEAT FROM CINEMA ) A WHERE (FREE=1) AND (PREVSEAT=1 OR NEXTSEAT =1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE,LEAD(FREE,1)OVER() NXT,LAG(FREE,1)OVER() PREV FROM CINEMA )A WHERE (FREE = NXT OR FREE = PREV) AND FREE=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, IFNULL(LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID),0) AS PREV, IFNULL(LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID),0) AS NEXT FROM CINEMA) T WHERE FREE = 1 AND (PREV = 1 OR NEXT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN (LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) - SEAT_ID = 1 OR SEAT_ID - (LAG(SEAT_ID) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) = 1 THEN SEAT_ID ELSE NULL END AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) X WHERE SEAT_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE CUR, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) NXT, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) PRV FROM CINEMA) AS C WHERE CUR = 1 AND (NXT = 1 OR PRV = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD (FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_NUM, LAG (FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_NUM FROM CINEMA ) SUB WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_NUM = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAG_NUM = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV FROM CINEMA )TMP WHERE (TMP.FREE=1 AND NEXT=1) OR (TMP.FREE=1 AND PREV=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE (SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) AND FREE=1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ( SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID -1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE - 0)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT *, LAG(FREE,1)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LA, LEAD(FREE,1)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEA FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (FREE=1 AND LA=1) OR (FREE=1 AND LEA=1) ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE) OVER() AS LAG1, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER() AS LEAD1 FROM CINEMA AS C) AS SUB WHERE (SUB.LAG1 = 1 AND SUB.FREE = 1) OR (SUB.FREE = 1 AND SUB.LEAD1)

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LAG (FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, LEAD (FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (PREV_FREE = 1 AND FREE =1) OR (FREE =1 AND NEXT_FREE =1) ORDER BY 1

SELECT T.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM ((SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.SEAT_ID + 1 = B.SEAT_ID AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ) UNION (SELECT B.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.SEAT_ID + 1 = B.SEAT_ID AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 )) AS T ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT T.SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (T.FREE = 1 AND PREV_FREE =1) OR (T.FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE = 1) ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS NEXT_SEAT,LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS BACK_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE =1 AND NEXT_SEAT=1) OR (FREE=1 AND BACK_SEAT =1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
WITH A AS(SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM A WHERE (SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM A) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM A)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH BASE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS L1, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS L2 FROM CINEMA ) SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C INNER JOIN BASE B ON B.SEAT_ID=C.SEAT_ID WHERE (C.FREE!=0 AND B.L1=1) OR (C.FREE!=0 AND B.L2=1)

WITH C_FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAST_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM C_FREE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAST_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER ( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) NEXT, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER ( ORDER BY SEAT_ID ) NEXTFREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE SEAT_ID+ 1 = NEXT AND FREE = 1 AND NEXTFREE = 1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT NEXT FROM CTE WHERE NEXT-1 = SEAT_ID AND FREE = 1 AND NEXTFREE = 1 ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, (SEAT_ID - RANK() OVER(ORDER BY FREE, SEAT_ID)) AS INV FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(SEAT_ID) OVER(PARTITION BY INV) AS CNT FROM CTE ) AS TAB WHERE CNT > 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(SEAT_ID) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LG, LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LD FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE ABS(SEAT_ID-LD) = 1 OR ABS(SEAT_ID-LG) = 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS RNK FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE RNK IN ( SELECT RNK FROM CTE GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2)

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LEAD(FREE) OVER() AS NEXT_, LAG(FREE) OVER() AS PREV_ FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NEXT_ = 1) OR (FREE= 1 AND PREV_ = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS NEXT_, LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS PREV_ FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NEXT_ = 1) OR (FREE= 1 AND PREV_ = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE) )

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS 1ST, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS 2ND FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE AS A WHERE (A.FREE = 1 AND A.1ST = 1) OR (A.FREE =1 AND A.2ND =1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(SEAT_ID)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEX_SEAT_ID, LAG(SEAT_ID)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE_SEAT_ID FROM CTE) A WHERE SEAT_ID-PRE_SEAT_ID=1 OR NEX_SEAT_ID-SEAT_ID=1

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER() FREE_NEXT FROM CINEMA), CTE2 AS( SELECT *, CASE WHEN FREE <> FREE_NEXT THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS IND FROM CTE1 ), CTE3 AS ( SELECT *,SUM(IND) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) CAT FROM CTE2 ), CTE4 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, COUNT(CAT) OVER(PARTITION BY CAT) CONT_NUM FROM CTE3 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE4 WHERE CONT_NUM >= 2 AND FREE = '1' ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE_1 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID , (SEAT_ID - DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS MARKING FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE ), CTE_2 AS ( SELECT * , COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY MARKING) AS CNT FROM CTE_1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE_2 WHERE CNT > 1

WITH CTE_FREE_SEATS AS( SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CTE_FREE_SEATS C1 INNER JOIN CTE_FREE_SEATS C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH FREE_SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM FREE_SEAT WHERE SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM FREE_SEAT) OR SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM FREE_SEAT) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH RANK_DIFFS AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - (ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC)) AS RANK_DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ), RANK_COUNTS AS ( SELECT RANK_DIFF, COUNT(*) AS RANK_COUNT FROM RANK_DIFFS GROUP BY RANK_DIFF ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM RANK_DIFFS WHERE RANK_DIFF IN (SELECT RANK_DIFF FROM RANK_COUNTS WHERE RANK_COUNT > 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH SEATS AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV, FREE AS CURR, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SEATS WHERE CURR <> 0 AND (PREV<>0 OR NEXT<>0)

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS L1, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS L2 FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE FREE=TRUE AND (L1=TRUE OR L2=TRUE) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH T1 AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LV1, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LG1 FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE (LV1 = 1 AND FREE=1) OR (LG1 =1 AND FREE=1) ORDER BY 1

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RNUM FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TEMP WHERE RNUM IN (SELECT RNUM FROM TEMP GROUP BY RNUM HAVING COUNT(*)>1)

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TEMP WHERE (LAG_SEAT=1 AND FREE=1) OR (LEAD_SEAT=1 AND FREE=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH TEMP AS(SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TEMP WHERE (PREV_FREE = 1 AND FREE = 1) OR (FREE =1 AND NEXT_FREE = 1)
WITH TMP AS ( SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE !=0) SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM TMP A JOIN TMP B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY 1

WITH VALID_SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NUM FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, COUNT(1) OVER(PARTITION BY SEAT_ID - NUM)AS C FROM VALID_SEAT)B WHERE C >=2

SELECT DISTINCT ORIGINAL.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS ORIGINAL JOIN CINEMA AS SELF_JOIN ON ABS(ORIGINAL.SEAT_ID - SELF_JOIN.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE ORIGINAL.FREE = '1' AND SELF_JOIN.FREE = '1' ORDER BY ORIGINAL.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE , LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA) AS TEMP WHERE (FREE=1 AND NEXT_FREE=1) OR (FREE=1 AND PREV_FREE=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A,CINEMA B WHERE ABS(B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND A.SEAT_ID +1 = B.SEAT_ID OR A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND A.SEAT_ID -1 = B.SEAT_ID ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY NUMBER) TOTAL_ROWS FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) NUMBER, SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) T0 ) T1 WHERE TOTAL_ROWS >= 2 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT S1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S1 JOIN CINEMA S2 ON ABS(S1.SEAT_ID - S2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE S1.FREE = 1 AND S2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY S1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A INNER JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC

WITH DATA1 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_NUM, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_NUM FROM CINEMA C ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM DATA1 WHERE FREE = 1 AND (PREV_NUM = 1 OR NEXT_NUM = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE A.FREE IS TRUE AND B.FREE IS TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE+C2.FREE=2 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH TMP AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, CASE WHEN (FREE = 1 AND LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END CC FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TMP WHERE CC = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT CINEMA.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA JOIN CINEMA C ON ABS(CINEMA.SEAT_ID - C.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE CINEMA.FREE = 1 AND C.FREE = 1 ORDER BY CINEMA.SEAT_ID
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER () NEXT , LAG(FREE, 1) OVER () PREVIOUS FROM CINEMA) C WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (C.FREE = C.NEXT OR C.FREE = C.PREVIOUS) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

WITH LEAD_LAG_SEAT AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE,LEAD(FREE,1,0) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_SEAT, LAG(FREE,1,0) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM LEAD_LAG_SEAT WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_SEAT = 1) OR (FREE=1 AND LAG_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREV_SEAT, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE = 1 AND (PREV_SEAT = 1 OR NEXT_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT W.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXTSEAT, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVSEAT FROM CINEMA ) AS W WHERE W.FREE = 1 AND W.NEXTSEAT = 1 OR W.FREE = 1 AND W.PREVSEAT = 1 ORDER BY W.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT * FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM TEMP A INNER JOIN TEMP B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM TEMP A INNER JOIN TEMP B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 ) A ORDER BY 1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE ,LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA)A WHERE FREE=1 AND (PREV_SEAT=1 OR NEXT_SEAT=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE != 0 AND B.FREE != 0 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ( SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) )
SELECT DISTINCT S.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S LEFT JOIN CINEMA N ON S.SEAT_ID=N.SEAT_ID-1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA P ON S.SEAT_ID=P.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE S.FREE=1 AND ( P.FREE=1 OR N.FREE=1)
WITH SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER () AS LAG_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER () AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SEAT WHERE FREE+LAG_SEAT = 2 OR FREE+LEAD_SEAT = 2

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_NUM, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_NUM FROM CINEMA) AS TEMP WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LAG_NUM = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LEAD_NUM = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT S1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA S1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA S2 ON S1.SEAT_ID = S2.SEAT_ID - 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA S3 ON S1.SEAT_ID = S3.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE S1.FREE = 1 AND (S2.FREE = 1 OR S3.FREE = 1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID - 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH TABLE1 AS (SELECT *, LAG(SEAT_ID, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LAST_SEAT_ID, LEAD(SEAT_ID, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) SELECT DISTINCT(SEAT_ID) FROM TABLE1 WHERE ((LAST_SEAT_ID IS NOT NULL) AND (LAST_SEAT_ID = SEAT_ID - 1)) OR ((NEXT_SEAT_ID IS NOT NULL) AND (NEXT_SEAT_ID = SEAT_ID + 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C WHERE FREE AND (EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID - 1 AND FREE ) OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID + 1 AND FREE ))
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) ORDER BY 1 ASC
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR C1.SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAGNUM, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEADNUM FROM CINEMA) AS TEMP WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LAGNUM = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LEADNUM = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1) OR (C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND C1.SEAT_ID-1=C2.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE >0 AND (SEAT_ID +1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE>0) OR SEAT_ID -1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE>0))
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER () NEXT , LAG(FREE) OVER () PREVIOUS FROM CINEMA) C WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (C.FREE = C.NEXT OR C.FREE = C.PREVIOUS) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH CTE AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) PREV , FREE CURR , LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) NEXT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE CURR = 1 AND (PREV = CURR OR CURR = NEXT)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE IS TRUE AND ( SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE IS TRUE) OR SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE IS TRUE) )
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS (C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE =1 AND C2.FREE =1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_FREE, LAG(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_FREE FROM CINEMA)C WHERE FREE=1 AND LEAD_FREE=1 OR FREE=1 AND LAG_FREE=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(T1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA T1 JOIN CINEMA T2 ON ABS(T1.SEAT_ID - T2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND T1.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 AND (SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NXT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE FROM CINEMA) AS TEMP WHERE (NXT>0 OR PRE>0) AND FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE =1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1) OR (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 AND (SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID) =1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE AND NEXT_SEAT) OR (FREE AND PREVIOUS_SEAT) ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ( (SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) OR (SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,COUNT(SEAT_ID) OVER(PARTITION BY GP ) AS CNT FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID-(ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS GP FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)A )B WHERE CNT>1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH T AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LEAD_FREE, LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LAG_FREE, FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM T WHERE T.FREE = 1 AND (T.LEAD_FREE = 1 OR T.LAG_FREE = 1) ORDER BY 1 ASC

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, FREE + IFNULL(LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID), 0) + IFNULL(LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID),0) AS SINGLE FROM CINEMA) )SUB WHERE SINGLE > 1 AND FREE != 0
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, CASE WHEN FREE = 1 AND ( FREE = LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) OR FREE = LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LAG_FREE FROM CINEMA) T WHERE LAG_FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = TRUE AND ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C2.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT * FROM (SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 AND C1.FREE = C2.FREE WHERE C1.FREE =1 UNION SELECT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 AND C1.FREE = C2.FREE WHERE C1.FREE =1)HFHF ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_SEAT, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA )AS SUB WHERE FREE = 1 AND (LAG_SEAT = FREE OR LEAD_SEAT=FREE)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ((A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID+1)OR(A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1)) AND (A.FREE=1) AND (B.FREE=1)
SELECT L.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) L JOIN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) R ON L.SEAT_ID = R.SEAT_ID - 1 OR L.SEAT_ID = R.SEAT_ID + 1 GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(SEAT_ID,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS L, LEAD(SEAT_ID,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS M FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1) A WHERE SEAT_ID -L = 1 OR M-SEAT_ID =1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID -B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT DISTINCT NEXT_FREE AS SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER() AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) R WHERE NEXT_FREE - SEAT_ID = 1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, LEAD(SEAT_ID) OVER() AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) R WHERE ABS(SEAT_ID - NEXT_FREE)=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE!=0 AND B.FREE!=0 AND ABS(B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE AND NEXT_SEAT OR FREE AND PREVIOUS_SEAT ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=TRUE AND B.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, COALESCE(LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID), 0) AS PREV_AV, COALESCE(LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID), 0) AS NEXT_AV FROM CINEMA) WINDOW_RES WHERE FREE = 1 AND PREV_AV + NEXT_AV > 0 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 AND ((SEAT_ID+1 IN ( SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 ) ) OR (SEAT_ID-1 IN ( SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 ) ) )
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID OR C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_FREE FROM CINEMA) A WHERE ((A.FREE - A.LAG_FREE) = 0 OR (A.FREE - A.LEAD_FREE) = 0) AND A.FREE = 1
WITH SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER () AS LAG_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER () AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SEAT WHERE FREE*LAG_SEAT = 1 OR FREE*LEAD_SEAT = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(C2.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE =1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SQ0 WHERE (FREE AND PREV_FREE) OR (FREE AND NEXT_FREE)

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) AS T1 WHERE (FREE=1 AND PREVIOUS_SEAT=1) OR (FREE=1 AND NEXT_SEAT=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID OR C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) WHERE C1.FREE = C2.FREE AND C1.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT TEMP1.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT A.SEAT_ID, (CASE WHEN B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 THEN TRUE WHEN B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID=-1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 THEN TRUE END) AS CONSECTIVE FROM CINEMA AS A , CINEMA AS B) AS TEMP1 WHERE CONSECTIVE='TRUE' ORDER BY TEMP1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM (CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B) WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = '1' AND B.FREE = '1' ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

WITH T1 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS LAST_FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE FREE = 1 AND (LAST_FREE=1 OR NEXT_FREE=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID -1) AND C1.FREE AND C2.FREE ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = TRUE AND C2.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT P1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA P1, CINEMA P2 WHERE P1.FREE = 1 AND P2.FREE = 1 AND (P1.SEAT_ID = P2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR P1.SEAT_ID + 1 = P2.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
WITH CTE AS ( (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1)) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT Y.SEAT_ID FROM CTE X,CTE Y WHERE ABS(X.SEAT_ID-Y.SEAT_ID)=1 ) Z
SELECT DISTINCT T1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA T1 JOIN CINEMA T2 ON ABS(T1.SEAT_ID - T2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND T1.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAGFREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEADINGFREE FROM CINEMA )A WHERE (FREE = 1 AND LEADINGFREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAGFREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.FREE=C2.FREE WHERE (C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID=1 OR C2.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID=1) AND C1.FREE=1 GROUP BY C1.SEAT_ID ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA) AS LOOKUP WHERE (PREV_SEAT OR NEXT_SEAT) AND FREE

SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) L1, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) L2 FROM CINEMA)A WHERE (A.FREE=1 AND A.L1=1) OR (A.FREE=1 AND A.L2=1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = TRUE AND C2.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
WITH CT AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS LD, LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS LG FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CT WHERE FREE*LD =1 OR FREE*LG = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) NEXT_FREE_SEAT , LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) PREV_FREE_SEAT FROM CINEMA) AS A WHERE (PREV_FREE_SEAT = 0 AND FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE_SEAT = 1) OR (PREV_FREE_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE_SEAT = 0) OR (PREV_FREE_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT A.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.SEAT_ID + 1 = B.SEAT_ID WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT B.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.SEAT_ID + 1 = B.SEAT_ID WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH AVAILABLE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM AVAILABLE WHERE FREE = 1 AND (LAG_SEAT = 1 OR LEAD_SEAT=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID -1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C ON A.SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID +1 WHERE (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE =1) OR (A.FREE =1 AND C.FREE =1)
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C2.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH T AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE,LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T WHERE ((NEXT_FREE =1 AND FREE = 1) OR (PREV_FREE =1 AND FREE = 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID=1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C ON C.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID=1 WHERE A.FREE = TRUE AND (B.FREE IS TRUE OR C.FREE IS TRUE) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA)A WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NEXT_SEAT = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND PREVIOUS_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT FREE, SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_SEAT FROM CINEMA) T WHERE (FREE + COALESCE(LAG_SEAT,0) + COALESCE(LEAD_SEAT,0)) >= 2 AND FREE > 0
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(B.SEAT_ID - A.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

WITH T_LEAD_LAG AS (SELECT LEAD(C.FREE) OVER(ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID) AS LEAD_ID, LAG(C.FREE) OVER(ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID) AS LAG_ID, C.SEAT_ID, C.FREE FROM CINEMA AS C ) SELECT CTE.SEAT_ID FROM T_LEAD_LAG AS CTE WHERE (CTE.LEAD_ID = 1 AND CTE.FREE = 1) OR (CTE.LAG_ID = 1 AND CTE.FREE = 1) ORDER BY CTE.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR (SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1))) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH ALL_DATA AS (SELECT CASE WHEN (FREE = 1 AND LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1) THEN SEAT_ID ELSE NULL END AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ALL_DATA WHERE SEAT_ID IS NOT NULL

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS AFTER , LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS BEFORE FROM CINEMA ) T WHERE T.FREE = 1 AND (T.FREE = T.AFTER OR T.FREE = T.BEFORE) ORDER BY 1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG1, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD1 FROM CINEMA ) AA WHERE FREE = 1 AND( LAG1 = 1 OR LEAD1 = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT(F.SEAT_ID) FROM ( (SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(SEAT_ID,1) OVER () AS NEXTS FROM CINEMA ) AS A LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.NEXTS =B.SEAT_ID WHERE B.FREE=A.FREE AND A.FREE=1 ) UNION ( SELECT A.NEXTS FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(SEAT_ID,1) OVER () AS NEXTS FROM CINEMA ) AS A LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.NEXTS =B.SEAT_ID WHERE B.FREE=A.FREE AND A.FREE=1 ) ) AS F ORDER BY F.SEAT_ID

WITH TMP AS (SELECT *, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM TMP WHERE FREE = TRUE AND PREV_SEAT = TRUE OR FREE = TRUE AND NEXT_SEAT = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT,LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE = 1 AND (PREVIOUS_SEAT = 1 OR NEXT_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ) A ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID , IFNULL(LAG(SEAT_ID, 1) OVER() , -1) AS PREVSEAT , IFNULL(LEAD(SEAT_ID, 1) OVER(),-1) AS NEXTSEAT FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ) T WHERE SEAT_ID = PREVSEAT + 1 OR SEAT_ID = NEXTSEAT-1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT C2.SEAT_ID SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) A ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH FREE_SEATS AS (SELECT SEATS.SEAT_ID AS CURRENT_SEAT, NEXT_SEATS.SEAT_ID AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA SEATS JOIN CINEMA NEXT_SEATS ON NEXT_SEATS.SEAT_ID - SEATS.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE SEATS.FREE = 1 AND NEXT_SEATS.FREE = 1) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA JOIN FREE_SEATS ON CINEMA.SEAT_ID = FREE_SEATS.CURRENT_SEAT OR CINEMA.SEAT_ID = FREE_SEATS.NEXT_SEAT ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(T1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA T1 JOIN CINEMA T2 ON ABS(T1.SEAT_ID - T2.SEAT_ID) =1 WHERE T1.FREE=1 AND T2.FREE=1 ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID+1=C2.SEAT_ID OR C2.SEAT_ID=C1.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1
SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = (B.SEAT_ID-1) LEFT JOIN CINEMA C ON A.SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND (B.FREE = 1 OR C.FREE =1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE IS TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT T.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS T INNER JOIN CINEMA AS T2 ON T.SEAT_ID = T2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR T.SEAT_ID = T2.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE T.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ) SELECT * FROM CTE ORDER BY CTE.SEAT_ID

WITH TMP AS (SELECT *, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TMP WHERE FREE = TRUE AND PREV_SEAT = TRUE OR FREE = TRUE AND NEXT_SEAT = TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH ADJACENT_SEATS AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ADJACENT_SEATS WHERE ADJACENT_SEATS.FREE = 1 AND (ADJACENT_SEATS.PREV_SEAT = 1 OR ADJACENT_SEATS.NEXT_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C LEFT JOIN CINEMA C1 ON C.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (C1.FREE = 1 OR C2.FREE = 1)
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = (C2.SEAT_ID - 1) LEFT JOIN CINEMA C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID = (C3.SEAT_ID + 1) WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C2.FREE = 1 OR C3.FREE = 1)

WITH TEMP AS (SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1, CINEMA AS C2 WHERE C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID && C1.FREE && C2.FREE), TEMP1 AS (SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1, CINEMA AS C2 WHERE C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID && C1.FREE && C2.FREE) SELECT * FROM (SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM TEMP AS T1 UNION SELECT T2.SEAT_ID FROM TEMP1 AS T2) AS F ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE, LAG(SEAT_ID) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT,LEAD(SEAT_ID)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ), PREVIOUS_FREE AS (SELECT CTE.SEAT_ID ,C1.FREE AS PREVIOUS_FREE_SEAT FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CTE ON C1.SEAT_ID = CTE.PREVIOUS_SEAT), NEXT_FREE AS ( SELECT CTE.SEAT_ID ,C1.FREE AS NEXT_FREE_SEAT FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CTE ON C1.SEAT_ID = CTE.NEXT_SEAT), FINAL_RESULT AS (SELECT CTE.SEAT_ID ,CTE.FREE ,CTE.NEXT_SEAT, N1.NEXT_FREE_SEAT , CTE.PREVIOUS_SEAT , P1.PREVIOUS_FREE_SEAT FROM CTE LEFT JOIN PREVIOUS_FREE P1 ON P1.SEAT_ID = CTE.SEAT_ID LEFT JOIN NEXT_FREE N1 ON N1.SEAT_ID = CTE.SEAT_ID) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM FINAL_RESULT WHERE FREE = 1 AND (NEXT_FREE_SEAT = 1 OR PREVIOUS_FREE_SEAT )
SELECT DISTINCT X.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA X, CINEMA Y WHERE ABS(X.SEAT_ID - Y.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND X.FREE = TRUE AND Y.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY X.SEAT_ID

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C WHERE EXISTS (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE (SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID + 1 AND FREE = 1) OR (SEAT_ID = C.SEAT_ID - 1 AND FREE = 1)) AND FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C2.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND C1.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C3.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C2.FREE = 1 OR C3.FREE = 1)
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID OR C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH CONSECUTIVE_SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CONSECUTIVE_SEAT WHERE PREVIOUS_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1 OR NEXT_SEAT = 1 AND FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH RANKED_SEATS AS ( SELECT CI.SEAT_ID, ROW_NUMBER () OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RNK FROM CINEMA CI WHERE CI.FREE = 1), CATEGORIZED_SEATS AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, RNK, SEAT_ID - RNK AS GRP FROM RANKED_SEATS) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CATEGORIZED_SEATS WHERE GRP IN (SELECT GRP FROM CATEGORIZED_SEATS GROUP BY GRP HAVING COUNT(1) > 1)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

WITH CTE1 AS (SELECT *, (SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1), CTE2 AS(SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY DIFF) AS CNT FROM CTE1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE2 WHERE CNT>1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1 AND ((SEAT_ID-1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1) OR (SEAT_ID + 1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE =1) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, (FREE-LEAD(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS DIFF_LEAD_FREE, (FREE-LAG(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS DIFF_LAG_FREE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE!=0 AND(DIFF_LEAD_FREE=0 OR DIFF_LAG_FREE=0)
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND A.FREE=TRUE AND B.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1,CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID+1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH ADJACENT_SEATS AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (PARTITION BY NULL ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (PARTITION BY NULL ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ADJACENT_SEATS WHERE ADJACENT_SEATS.FREE = 1 AND (ADJACENT_SEATS.PREV_SEAT = 1 OR ADJACENT_SEATS.NEXT_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RN, (SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE ='1') SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE DIFF IN (SELECT DIFF FROM CTE GROUP BY DIFF HAVING COUNT(*)>=2)
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A, CINEMA AS B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND ( A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID+1 OR A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1) AND B.FREE=1
SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY B.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) =1 AND A.FREE=TRUE AND B.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER() AS LEADROW, LAG(FREE) OVER() AS LAGROW FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE=1 AND LEADROW=1) OR (FREE=1 AND LAGROW=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID =1 OR C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = -1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE * C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID =1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT * FROM ( (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA) AS N WHERE FREE = NEXT_FREE AND FREE = 1) UNION (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_FREE FROM CINEMA) AS P WHERE FREE = PREV_FREE AND FREE = 1) ) AS C ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NXT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRV FROM CINEMA ) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE = 1 AND PRV = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND NXT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = '1' AND C2.FREE='1' AND (C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID=1) GROUP BY C1.SEAT_ID ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG1, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG2 FROM CINEMA ) AS T1 WHERE (T1.LAG1=1 AND T1.FREE=1) OR (T1.LAG2=1 AND T1.FREE=1) ORDER BY T1.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 AND ((SEAT_ID+1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) OR (SEAT_ID-1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1) )
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C LEFT JOIN CINEMA C1 ON C.SEAT_ID -1 = C1.SEAT_ID LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C.SEAT_ID +1 = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C.FREE AND (COALESCE(C1.FREE,FALSE) OR COALESCE(C2.FREE,FALSE))
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID)= 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1,CINEMA C2 WHERE (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1) AND C1.FREE =1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ( C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 ) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LEAD(FREE) OVER () AS NEXT_FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER () AS LAST_FREE FROM CINEMA) AS A WHERE (FREE = 1 AND NEXT_FREE = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LAST_FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER () AS ROW_DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(SEAT_ID) OVER (PARTITION BY ROW_DIFF) AS NUM FROM CTE) A WHERE NUM > 1

SELECT X.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAST_FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA ) AS X WHERE (X.FREE = 1 AND X.LAST_FREE = 1) OR (X.FREE = 1 AND X.NEXT_FREE = 1) ORDER BY X.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE AND ( SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE) OR SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE) )

SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, LAG(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG1, LEAD(FREE)OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD1,FREE FROM CINEMA)A WHERE (A.FREE=1 AND A.LAG1=1) OR (A.FREE=1 AND A.LEAD1=1) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *,LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA) AS LOOKUP WHERE FREE AND (PREV_SEAT OR NEXT_SEAT) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1) WHERE C1.FREE != 0 AND C2.FREE != 0 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, SUM(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ROWS BETWEEN 1 PRECEDING AND 1 FOLLOWING) SM FROM CINEMA) T1 WHERE T1.SM > 1 AND T1.FREE = 1 ORDER BY 1 ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE AND B.FREE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT *, LEAD(FREE) OVER() BEF, LAG(FREE) OVER() AFT FROM CINEMA) AS T1 WHERE FREE = 1 AND (BEF = 1 OR AFT = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE AND (ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID)=1 AND B.FREE) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON (A.SEAT_ID-1 = B.SEAT_ID) OR (A.SEAT_ID+1 = B.SEAT_ID) WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1 ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV, LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT FROM CINEMA) SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE = 1 AND PREV = FREE OR FREE = 1 AND NEXT = FREE ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE = TRUE AND C2.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH CTE_FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE , LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS BE , LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS AF FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE_FREE WHERE FREE + BE = 2 OR FREE + AF = 2
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID +1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID -1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT T.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS T INNER JOIN CINEMA AS T2 ON ABS(T.SEAT_ID - T2.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND T.FREE = 1 AND T2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA AS A LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE A.FREE=B.FREE AND A.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 UNION SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1) T1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT CASE WHEN (LAG(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1 AND FREE = 1) THEN SEAT_ID WHEN (LEAD(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) = 1 AND FREE = 1) THEN SEAT_ID ELSE NULL END AS CONSECUTIVE_SEATS FROM CINEMA) SELECT CONSECUTIVE_SEATS AS SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE CONSECUTIVE_SEATS IS NOT NULL
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND A.SEAT_ID + 1 = B.SEAT_ID OR A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND A.SEAT_ID - 1 = B.SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS PREVIOUS_NODE, LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) AS NEXT_NODE FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE AND PREVIOUS_NODE) OR (FREE AND NEXT_NODE) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT (C1.SEAT_ID ) FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON ABS(C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH TEMP AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)LG, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID)LD FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TEMP WHERE (FREE=1 AND LG=1) OR (FREE=1 AND LD=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER() AS PREV_ROW, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER() AS NEXT_ROW FROM CINEMA) AS SUB WHERE (FREE - NEXT_ROW = 0 OR FREE - PREV_ROW = 0) AND FREE!=0

WITH CTE AS(SELECT SEAT_ID, IF(FREE = 1 AND (LEAD(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) = 1 OR LAG(FREE, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC) = 1), 1, 0) AS WHATIF FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE WHATIF = 1
SELECT DISTINCT(C1.SEAT_ID) FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1,CINEMA C2,CINEMA C3 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 OR ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C3.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C3.FREE=1 ORDER BY 1
WITH T1 AS( SELECT *, SEAT_ID-1 FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE=1 ) SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM T1 WHERE T1.SEAT_ID-1 IN (SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM T1) OR T1.SEAT_ID+1 IN (SELECT T1.SEAT_ID FROM T1)

WITH SEAT AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, SUM(FREE) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)-SEAT_ID AS GAP FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SEAT WHERE GAP IN (SELECT GAP FROM SEAT WHERE FREE = 1 GROUP BY GAP HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) AND FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LAG, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS FREE_LEAD FROM CINEMA) AS C WHERE (FREE=1 AND FREE_LAG=1) OR (FREE=1 AND FREE_LEAD=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH JOINED AS ( SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS SEAT1, C2.SEAT_ID AS SEAT2 FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT1 AS SEAT_ID FROM JOINED UNION SELECT SEAT2 AS SEAT_ID FROM JOINED) TMP ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH T AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) L1, LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) LAG1 FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T WHERE FREE=1 AND (L1 = 1 OR LAG1 = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH INFO AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, SUM(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ROWS BETWEEN 1 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) AS PREV_CURR, SUM(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID ROWS BETWEEN CURRENT ROW AND 1 FOLLOWING) AS CURR_NEXT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM INFO WHERE PREV_CURR=2 OR CURR_NEXT=2
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON (C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID -1 OR C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID + 1 ) AND C2.FREE =1 AND C1.FREE =1

SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, COALESCE(LEAD(FREE) OVER(), !FREE) NEXT , COALESCE(LAG(FREE) OVER(), !FREE) PREVIOUS FROM CINEMA ) C WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (C.FREE = C.NEXT OR C.FREE = C.PREVIOUS) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID OR C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 GROUP BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS PREV ON C.SEAT_ID = PREV.SEAT_ID + 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA AS NEXT ON C.SEAT_ID = NEXT.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C.FREE AND ( PREV.FREE <=> 1 OR NEXT.FREE <=> 1 )
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ( (SEAT_ID - 1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR (SEAT_ID + 1) IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 WHERE C1.FREE =1 AND (1= (SELECT C2.FREE FROM CINEMA C2 WHERE C2.SEAT_ID =C1.SEAT_ID+1 ) OR (SELECT C3.FREE FROM CINEMA C3 WHERE C3.SEAT_ID =C1.SEAT_ID-1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 , CINEMA C2 WHERE 1 = 1 AND ( C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ) AND ( C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID -1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID +1 ) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
