WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS GRP FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, COUNT(SEAT_ID) OVER(PARTITION BY GRP) AS NM FROM CTE) A WHERE A.NM >= 2 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE + B.FREE = 2 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ( SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) OR SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC

WITH T1 AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RN, SEAT_ID-(ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID)) AS DIFF FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE != 0 ),T2 AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID,COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY DIFF) AS CNT FROM T1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM T2 WHERE CNT >= 2 ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1,CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 AND ABS(C2.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY 1 ASC
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1) AND (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1) ) AS P

WITH CC AS ( SELECT C.*,(SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC)) AS ID_ROW_DIFF FROM CINEMA C WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY ID_ROW_DIFF) AS TOTALCOUNT FROM CC ) ITM WHERE TOTALCOUNT > 1

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER() AS NEXT_ONE_AVAIL, LAG(FREE) OVER() AS PREV_ONE_AVAIL FROM CINEMA) PREVS WHERE FREE = 1 AND (PREV_ONE_AVAIL = 1 OR NEXT_ONE_AVAIL = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1, CINEMA AS C2 WHERE ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND (SEAT_ID-1 IN ( SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) OR SEAT_ID+1 IN ( SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ))
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 AND ((SEAT_ID -1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)) OR (SEAT_ID +1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1)))
WITH DATA AS ( SELECT * FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM DATA WHERE (SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM DATA)) OR (SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM DATA)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT DISTINCT C2.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2, CINEMA C3 WHERE (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID+1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1) OR (C3.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND C3.FREE = 1) ORDER BY C2.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B, CINEMA C WHERE A.FREE!=0 AND B.FREE!=0 AND (A.SEAT_ID-1=B.SEAT_ID OR A.SEAT_ID+1=B.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE AND (SEAT_ID + 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE) OR SEAT_ID - 1 IN (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = TRUE) ) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C LEFT JOIN CINEMA C1 ON C.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID - 1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND (C1.FREE = 1 OR C2.FREE = 1)

SELECT NEWTABLE.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE,LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXTSEAT , LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUSSEAT FROM CINEMA) AS NEWTABLE WHERE NEWTABLE.FREE = 1 AND NEWTABLE.NEXTSEAT = 1 OR NEWTABLE.FREE = 1 AND NEWTABLE.PREVIOUSSEAT = 1 ORDER BY NEWTABLE.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXTSEAT, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVSEAT FROM CINEMA) AS X WHERE X.FREE = 1 AND X.NEXTSEAT = 1 OR X.FREE = 1 AND X.PREVSEAT = 1 ORDER BY X.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = TRUE AND C2.FREE = TRUE AND ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID) = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C JOIN CINEMA C1 ON ABS(C.SEAT_ID-C1.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C.FREE=1 AND C1.FREE=1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT *, LAG(FREE) OVER () AS PREVIOUS, LEAD(FREE) OVER () AS LATER FROM CINEMA) A WHERE (FREE = 1 AND PREVIOUS = 1) OR (FREE = 1 AND LATER = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

SELECT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C3 ON C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C3.SEAT_ID LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND (C2.FREE = 1 OR C3.FREE = 1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE != 0 AND C2.FREE !=0 AND (C1.SEAT_ID - 1 = C2.SEAT_ID OR C1.SEAT_ID + 1 = C2.SEAT_ID) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 WHERE (C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID + 1 OR C2.SEAT_ID = C1.SEAT_ID - 1) AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1

WITH INCLUDE_SURROUNDING_SEATS AS( SELECT C.SEAT_ID, C.FREE, LEAD(C.FREE, 1) OVER () AS NEXT_SEAT , LAG(C.FREE, 1) OVER () AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA C ) SELECT SS.SEAT_ID FROM INCLUDE_SURROUNDING_SEATS SS WHERE SS.FREE = 1 AND (SS.NEXT_SEAT = 1 OR SS.PREV_SEAT = 1) ORDER BY SS.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1, CINEMA C2 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 AND (C2.SEAT_ID - C1.SEAT_ID = 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID = 1) ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS (SELECT *, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS RN FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE>0 ) , CTE2 AS (SELECT *,COUNT(*) OVER(PARTITION BY RN) AS C FROM CTE) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE2 WHERE C>=2
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID+1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTS AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD1, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG1 FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTS WHERE (LEAD1 = 1 AND FREE = 1) OR (LAG1 = 1 AND FREE = 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS C1 INNER JOIN CINEMA AS C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID - C2.SEAT_ID ) = 1 AND C1.FREE = 1 AND C2.FREE = 1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE, LAG(FREE, 1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE_FREE FROM CINEMA) SUB WHERE SUB.FREE > 0 AND SUB.FREE + IFNULL(SUB.NEXT_FREE,0) + IFNULL(SUB.PRE_FREE, 0) >= 2 ORDER BY SEAT_ID

(SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1 AND A.FREE=B.FREE WHERE 1=1 AND A.FREE=1 UNION SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID+1 AND A.FREE=B.FREE WHERE 1=1 AND A.FREE=1) ORDER BY 1

WITH DATA AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREVIOUS_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM DATA WHERE FREE * NEXT_SEAT = 1 OR FREE * PREVIOUS_SEAT = 1
WITH TMP AS( SELECT SEAT_ID , FREE , LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NXT , LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PRE FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM TMP WHERE FREE*PRE=1 OR FREE*NXT=1

SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT P.SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE FROM CINEMA)P WHERE P.FREE= 1 AND P.NEXT_FREE = 1 UNION SELECT P.NEXT_SEAT FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_FREE, LEAD(SEAT_ID,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT FROM CINEMA)P WHERE P.FREE= 1 AND P.NEXT_FREE = 1) A ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 WHERE C1.FREE =1 AND C2.FREE =1 ORDER BY C1.SEAT_ID ASC

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NFREE, LAG(FREE) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PFREE FROM CINEMA ) Z WHERE (FREE=NFREE AND FREE=1) OR (FREE=PFREE AND FREE=1) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1

WITH T AS (SELECT CASE WHEN T1.FREE = 1 AND ((SELECT FREE FROM CINEMA WHERE SEAT_ID = T1.SEAT_ID-1 AND FREE = 1) OR ((SELECT FREE FROM CINEMA WHERE SEAT_ID = T1.SEAT_ID+1 AND FREE = 1))) THEN T1.SEAT_ID ELSE NULL END AS C_SEATS FROM CINEMA T1) SELECT C_SEATS AS SEAT_ID FROM T WHERE C_SEATS IS NOT NULL

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT A.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID_LOW, B.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID_HIGH, A.FREE AS FREE_LOW, B.FREE AS FREE_HIGH FROM CINEMA A LEFT JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 ) SELECT SEAT_ID_LOW AS SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE_LOW = 1 AND FREE_HIGH = 1 UNION SELECT SEAT_ID_HIGH AS SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE FREE_LOW = 1 AND FREE_HIGH = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 AND (A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID=1 OR B.SEAT_ID-A.SEAT_ID=1) ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID-B.SEAT_ID)=1 ORDER BY 1
WITH SEAT_FREE AS ( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE,LAG(FREE) OVER() AS PREV, LEAD(FREE) OVER() AS NEXT FROM CINEMA ) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM SEAT_FREE WHERE FREE=1 AND (PREV=1 OR NEXT=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID

WITH CTE AS( SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, SEAT_ID - ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS GRP FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = '1') SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE GRP IN (SELECT GRP FROM CTE GROUP BY GRP HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY B.SEAT_ID

SELECT * FROM ( SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 UNION SELECT B.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1) C ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID

SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT *, LAG(FREE,1) OVER( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LAG1 , LEAD(FREE,1) OVER( ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS LEAD1 FROM CINEMA ) C WHERE (C.FREE = 1) AND ((C.FREE = C.LAG1) OR ( C.FREE = C.LEAD1)) ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT SEAT_ID FROM (SELECT A.SEAT_ID, A.FREE FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON A.FREE = B.FREE WHERE A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 ) AS TEMP WHERE TEMP.FREE = 1

SELECT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A INNER JOIN CINEMA B ON A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 UNION SELECT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C INNER JOIN CINEMA D ON C.SEAT_ID = D.SEAT_ID - 1 WHERE C.FREE = 1 AND D.FREE = 1 ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C1.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 JOIN CINEMA C2 ON ABS(C1.SEAT_ID-C2.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C1.FREE=TRUE AND C2.FREE=TRUE ORDER BY 1
SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C1 WHERE C1.FREE = 1 AND EXISTS( SELECT * FROM CINEMA C2 WHERE FREE = 1 AND (C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID - 1 OR C1.SEAT_ID = C2.SEAT_ID + 1)) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND (A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1) ORDER BY 1

WITH SEAT_PAIR AS (SELECT C1.SEAT_ID AS ID1, C2.SEAT_ID AS ID2 FROM CINEMA C1 LEFT JOIN CINEMA C2 ON C1.SEAT_ID=C2.SEAT_ID-1 AND C1.FREE=1 AND C2.FREE=1 WHERE C2.FREE IS NOT NULL) SELECT ID1 AS SEAT_ID FROM SEAT_PAIR UNION SELECT ID2 AS SEAT_ID FROM SEAT_PAIR ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA AS A JOIN CINEMA AS B ON A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID+1 OR A.SEAT_ID=B.SEAT_ID-1 WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID

SELECT SEAT_ID FROM ( SELECT SEAT_ID,FREE,LAG(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS P_SEAT, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER(ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS F_SEAT FROM CINEMA ) A WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND A.P_SEAT=1 OR A.FREE=1 AND A.F_SEAT = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
WITH A AS (SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA WHERE FREE = 1) SELECT DISTINCT A1.SEAT_ID FROM A A1, A A2 WHERE A1.SEAT_ID = A2.SEAT_ID + 1 OR A1.SEAT_ID = A2.SEAT_ID - 1
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE + B.FREE = 2 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT C.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA C JOIN CINEMA D ON ABS(C.SEAT_ID-D.SEAT_ID)=1 AND C.FREE = TRUE AND D.FREE = TRUE ORDER BY C.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B ON ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = TRUE AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC

WITH CTE AS (SELECT SEAT_ID, FREE, LEAD(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS NEXT_SEAT, LAG(FREE,1) OVER (ORDER BY SEAT_ID) AS PREV_SEAT FROM CINEMA) SELECT SEAT_ID FROM CTE WHERE (FREE=1 AND NEXT_SEAT=1) OR (FREE=1 AND PREV_SEAT=1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A JOIN CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE=1 AND B.FREE=1 AND ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) =1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID
SELECT DISTINCT A.SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE ABS(A.SEAT_ID - B.SEAT_ID) = 1 AND A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 ORDER BY A.SEAT_ID ASC
SELECT DISTINCT(A.SEAT_ID) AS SEAT_ID FROM CINEMA A, CINEMA B WHERE A.FREE = 1 AND B.FREE = 1 AND (A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID + 1 OR A.SEAT_ID = B.SEAT_ID - 1) ORDER BY SEAT_ID
